245-and-wish-i-never-met-you-as-part-of-prison-tapes-series-3778937">Tory Lanez 发布新歌“Cell 245”和“Wish I Never Met You”作为“Prison Tapes”系列的一部分，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
聆听 Bright Eyes 的“朋克摇滚”和受 Beastie Boys 启发的新单曲“Rainbow Overpass” https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-share-new-single-rainbow-overpass-announce-us-tour-dates-3781778?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bright-eyes-share-新单彩虹立交桥宣布美国巡演日期Liberty DunworthWed, 07 Aug 2024 14:51:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3781778 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="明亮的眼睛，2024" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队还宣布了一系列北美巡演日期</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-share-new-single-rainbow-overpass-announce-us-tour-dates-3781778">Listen to Bright Eyes 的“朋克摇滚”和受 Beastie Boys 启发的新单曲“Rainbow Overpass”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="明亮的眼睛，2024" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Bright-eyes@2000x1280-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bright-eyes">Bright Eyes</a>带着受朋克摇滚启发的新单曲“Rainbow Overpass”回来了 - 请查看下面的内容，以及新宣布的美国巡演日期。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/bright-eyes-down-in-the-weeds-where-the-world-once-was-album-review-2730449">明亮的眼睛——《世界曾经的杂草丛中》评论：近十年后传奇回归</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲是这支美国独立摇滚乐队从他们即将发行的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-announce-new-album-five-dice-all-threes-with-single-bells-whistles-and-uk-and-european-tour-3768595">“Five Dice, All Threes”</a>中分享的最新单曲，该专辑将于 9 月 20 日通过 Dead Oceans 发行。</p><p>继上个月发布的主打单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-announce-new-album-five-dice-all-threes-with-single-bells-whistles-and-uk-and-european-tour-3768595">“Bells &amp; Whistles”</a>之后，即将推出的 LP 的最新预告片采用了更加激烈、高能量的方式——利用了朋克场景的同样的活力和强度。</p><p>在原声吉他、喇叭和 The So So Glos 的 Alex Orange Drink 令人难忘的歌声的推动下，最终的结果向 Beastie Boys 等艺术家致敬。</p><p> “亚历克斯和我一起写了很多歌曲，但‘彩虹立交桥’是他唯一能[唱]一首诗的。他有点像我的炒作人，让野兽男孩来搞事情，”主唱康纳·奥伯斯特 (Conor Oberst) 说道。</p><p> “他们是在朋克摇滚和 Beasties 的陪伴下长大的，所以有很多其他声音的小爆发。我喜欢。它创造能量。有时，音乐可能会让人感觉平淡，直到你进入现场，充满肾上腺素和原始能量。我没有像我们巡演时那样进行相反的工作，而是试图将一些能量记录到唱片中。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="彩虹立交桥" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/n2JFZdah9YU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>如前所述，这张新专辑将于下个月发布，并将成为乐队继 2020 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/bright-eyes-down-in-the-weeds-where-the-world-once-was-album-review-2730449">《Down In The WeedsWhere The World Once Was》</a>之后的第十张录音室专辑。</p><p>除了 Alex Orange Drink 之外，该项目还将邀请<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cat-power">Cat Power</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-berninger">Matt Berninger</a>等嘉宾担任嘉宾。您可以<a href="https://brighteyes.lnk.to/Five-Dice-All-Threes" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订/预先保存。</p><p> “《五骰子，全三》由内布拉斯加州奥马哈的 ARC 工作室自行制作和录制，是一张不同寻常的强度和温柔、集体驱魔和个人挖掘的唱片。当然，这些品质是粉丝们在 Bright Eyes 职业生涯近三十年以来所期待的品质，”LP 的新闻稿中写道。</p><p> “尽管背后有着丰富的历史，这些新歌仍散发出一种发自内心的兴奋，这是他们以前从未尝试过的，”它补充道。 “在《五个骰子，全是三个》中，有时你可能会为他感到担心；其他时候，他似乎是唯一一个能够清楚地帮助我们摆脱困境的人。”</p><p>在上个月宣布这张专辑后，Bright Eyes 还透露了 2024 年晚些时候在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-announce-new-album-five-dice-all-threes-with-single-bells-whistles-and-uk-and-european-tour-3768595">英国和欧洲举办的一系列演出</a>的细节。</p><p>他们将于 11 月在伍尔弗汉普顿和伦敦进行两场英国演出，然后前往欧洲大陆的各个城市，包括奈梅亨、根特、科隆、柏林和斯德哥尔摩。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8plnUyPVJ6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" str